window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Three amateur sleuths....three small towns....one bundle of cozy mysteries.</p> <p><i>Pains and Penalties</i></p> <p>Kalina Greystone’s return home brings back old friends and even older secrets. Her great aunt's murder pushes her to snoop where she doesn’t belong. As she digs into her aunt’s past, she uncovers a dark truth the killer wants revealed. Will she stop the spree before the killer’s thirst for vengeance is sated?</p> <p><i>Into the Lion's Den</i></p> <p>Reverend Margot Quade never expected to be dropped in the midst of a murder. She just wanted to get reacquainted with her hometown of Port Marie, Vermont, maybe find her place in the world again after serving her tour of duty. But when a friendly dinner with a member of her unit turns deadly, she's pulled into a mystery she can't help but solve.</p> <p><i>High Noon</i></p> <p>When one of her coworkers turns up dead, witch Darcy Ingram becomes the prime suspect — and sets out to clear her name with the help of some paranormal companions! Her magic leads on the hunt for the real killer. But is Darcy willing to risk her new beginning to out the real perpetrator?</p> <p>S. E. Biglow's Cozy Mystery Starter Pack contains the first book in each of her cozy mystery series. From sleuthing shopkeepers and inquisitive reverends to magical mysteries, this collection has something for every cozy mystery lover.</p>"; 
